</ul>
</section>
<section data-depth="1" id="fs-id1170572597916" class="section-exercises">
<p id="fs-id1170572597920">In the following exercises, use the limit laws to evaluate each limit. Justify each step by indicating the appropriate limit law(s).</p>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-id1170572597924">
<div data-type="problem" id="fs-id1170572597926">
